snippet.title: Coke Studio & Dastaangoi present Umair Jaswal
snippet.description: We invite you to take a closer look into the evolution of Umair Jaswal. Listen to him talk about the year 2020, his travel experiences and the how it impacted his perception of the world. Umair also gives an exclusive inside look at “Har Funn Maula” and how it all came together, by a conversation with Rohail about his journey on the road.
